      "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
      "name": "Soul Steal",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The akaruzug unleashes a blast of negative energy that tears the souls of its victims. Any creature within 20 feet of the akaruzug must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:34] save. The akaruzug can't use soul steal again for [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> No effect</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 3}.</p>"
        },
